# Project Overview

This project is a Learning Management System built with:
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- React Router
- Tanstack Query
- Supabase

## Key Files and Directories

- [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx) - Main application component with routing configuration
- [src/pages](mdc:src/pages) - All page components
- [src/components](mdc:src/components) - Reusable UI components
- [src/contexts](mdc:src/contexts) - React context providers
- [src/hooks](mdc:src/hooks) - Custom React hooks
- [src/services](mdc:src/services) - API and service functions
- [src/lib](mdc:src/lib) - Utility libraries and configurations

## Application Structure

The application follows a modular structure with separate directories for components, pages, hooks, and services. It uses React Router for navigation and has authentication features provided by AuthContext.